<plot>The Lost Journal of Vice Marceaux is a 12 minute short film about a man who makes an amazing discovery that could potentially prove the soul exists. Desperate for anything concrete to give meaning to the suffering of a disease that took his family, Vice becomes obsessed. As his humanity drains away, he forgets about his family and becomes capable of a terrible crime.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?572471</url></doc>
